<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3680] Java async processor fails to notify errors to clients</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3680</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Unlike its sync counter part, Java async processor has been ignoring any errors.&lt;br/&gt;
It turned out that it was actually trying to send errors back and failing to do so because of other bugs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
